Package: nflmetamodel
Type: Package
Title: NFL Meta-Model for Calibrated Win Probabilities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Derek", "Debellis", email = "derek@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A reproducible NFL meta-model that learns when market and model
    probabilities are miscalibrated conditional on context, producing weekly
    calibrated win probabilities with monitoring.
